Nitu Travels Baileys Gateway v2.1.0

Website integration changes:
- Oracle minute worker authenticates to whatsapp-gateway-worker.php with x-api-key.
- Delivery callbacks include x-api-key in addition to the existing HMAC signature.
- Bounded POST /api/v1/messages/statuses accepts up to 100 UUIDs for repair synchronization.

Cutover safety:
- Existing backlog is persistently paused on first v2.1 startup.
- Administrator may pause or resume delivery explicitly.
- Individual queued/retry rows may be cancelled before transmission.
- All queued/retry rows may be cancelled in one guarded action.
- Pairing WhatsApp does not release stale messages until delivery is resumed.

Companion website release: Manage Nitu Travels v15.10.
